title: Jim Raney_Jim Hall_Zoot Sims / 2 JIMS AND ZOOT / 1964
description:
This LP has been re-issued several times but it is still a rarity.





        2 JIMS AND ZOOT    (1964)




JIM RANEY...................guitar

JIM HALL....................guitar

ZOOT SIMS...................tenor

STEVE SWALLOW...............bass

OSIE JOHNSON................Drums



Steve Swallow is one of those "barometer musicians" whose presence indicates the

high likelihood of great music
